v class="push-item__ratings"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-average-text"><div class="fivestar-static-form-item"><div class="form-item form-type-item"><div class="field-main"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">5</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="on"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="description"><p class="fivestar-summary fivestar-summary-">(1<span class="rating-text"> rating</span>)</p></div></div></div></div></div> </article></li></ul></div></div></div> </section> <section id="block-bbcgf-search-views-bbcgf-recipe-carousel" class="section-box section-box--related-recipe-carousel block block-bbcgf-search-views"> <header class="section-box__header"><h2 class="section-box__title"></h2> </header><div class="section-box__content"> <aside class="section-box section-box--interstitial section-box--interstitial--swiper"> <header class="section-box__header"><h2 class="section-box__title">Related content</h2> </header><div class="section-box__content"><div class="swiper-container"><div class="swiper-wrapper"> <article id="node-3519511" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-guide node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/howto/guide/how-make-our-fudgy-chocolate-and-orange-gateau"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/guide-main-image.jpg?itok=uisTpaxs" width="468" height="382" alt="Fudgy chocolate and orange gateau" title="Fudgy chocolate and orange gateau" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Guide</span></div><h3 cla